nagement\\n\\n**5 ideas created** for the \\\"Credential & Secret Management\\\" context:\\n\\n| # | Title | Category | Effort | Impact | Risk |\\n|---|-------|----------|--------|--------|------|\\n| 1 | Wrap decrypt() with DecryptionError and timing | code_quality | 2 | 8 | 2 |\\n| 2 | Add cache hit/miss metrics to TenantKeyManager | functionality | 3 | 7 | 1 |\\n| 3 | Audit credential deletion and access operations | code_quality | 2 | 9 | 2 |\\n| 4 | Add error handling to maintainCache() timer | code_quality | 1 | 7 | 1 |\\n| 5 | Expose credential file gauge and cleanup metrics | functionality | 2 | 6 | 1 |\\n\\n### Key observations:\\n\\n- **Biggest gap**: Credential deletion and access leave no audit trail despite audit infrastructure already existing - only creation is logged (idea #3, highest impact)\\n- **Silent failure risk**: `maintainCache()` in TenantKeyManager has no try/catch around its async work - a single failed derivation causes an unobserved promise rejection (idea #4, easiest fix)\\n- **Unused abstraction**: `DecryptionError` class exists in crypto.ts with rich context fields but `decrypt()` never uses it - raw crypto errors propagate instead (idea #1)\\n- **Invisible metrics**: Both the key cache (hit/miss rates) and credential file lifecycle (active file count) have no external visibility despite being security-critical subsystems\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":3282,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":46630,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":3282},\"output_tokens\":1,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"6b375ece-41c0-48fe-9151-de360e723e96\",\"uuid\":\"17a6a8e2-ceb0-41f7-bc33-38509428540b\"}\n[2026-03-18T11:54:05.358Z] [STDOUT] {\"type\":\"result\",\"subtype\":\"success\",\"is_error\":false,\"duration_ms\":140556,\"duration_api_ms\":124229,\"num_turns\":22,\"result\":\"All 5 ideas saved successfully. Here's the summary:\\n\\n## Observability Scout - Credential & Secret Management\\n\\n**5 ideas created** for the \\\"Credential & Secret Management\\\" context:\\n\\n| # | Title | Category | Effort | Impact | Risk |\\n|---|-------|----------|--------|--------|------|\\n| 1 | Wrap decrypt() with DecryptionError and timing | code_quality | 2 | 8 | 2 |\\n| 2 | Add cache hit/miss metrics to TenantKeyManager | functionality | 3 | 7 | 1 |\\n| 3 | Audit credential deletion and access operations | code_quality | 2 | 9 | 2 |\\n| 4 | Add error handling to maintainCache() timer | code_quality | 1 | 7 | 1 |\\n| 5 | Expose credential file gauge and cleanup metrics | functionality | 2 | 6 | 1 |\\n\\n### Key observations:\\n\\n- **Biggest gap**: Credential deletion and access leave no audit trail despite audit infrastructure already existing - only creation is logged (idea #3, highest impact)\\n- **Silent failure risk**: `maintainCache()` in TenantKeyManager has no try/catch around its async work - a single failed derivation causes an unobserved promise rejection (idea #4, easiest fix)\\n- **Unused abstraction**: `DecryptionError` class exists in crypto.ts with rich context fields but `decrypt()` never uses it - raw crypto errors propagate instead (idea #1)\\n- **Invisible metrics**: Both the key cache (hit/miss rates) and credential file lifecycle (active file count) have no external visibility despite being security-critical subsystems\",\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"session_id\":\"6b375ece-41c0-48fe-9151-de360e723e96\",\"total_cost_usd\":0.5595622499999999,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":13,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":34403,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":355357,\"output_tokens\":6672,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":34403,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterat